{
  "id": "ferromancy-tree",
  "paradigmId": "ferromancy",
  "name": "The Art of Ferromancy",
  "description": "Burn metals to gain supernatural powers. Bloodline determines which metals you can burn.",
  "lore": "Ferromancy is genetic - you either have the blood, or you don't. Those with\nFerromancer ancestry may be MonoResonants (one metal) or OmniResonant (all metals).\nBut the power lies dormant until The Fracture - a moment of intense trauma\nthat breaks the barriers and lets the power through.",
